item.title: dsHistory, v1-pre r32
item.description: New home, much better performance, plenty of bug fixes, complete documentation, and more!

item.title: dsHistory, v1-beta1
item.description: This is the first beta release, but there's still a ton of work to do, so please be patient. This release contains a bug fix for Gecko when trying to add function to stack after bindQueryVars was called and back button had been clicked. Support for Safari 3 has also been added. Safari 2 and Opera, here I come....

item.title: dsHistory, v1-beta4 is out now
item.description: dsHistory v1-beta4 is out. It contains a number of small bug fixes since the last release. You can download it from the project's home.
